{"tid":2201133,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"花心女警「一腳踏兩船」 遭打傷 新歡男警涉普通襲擊被捕 事隔近一個月男警終被起訴 明日觀塘裁判法院提堂","createTime":"2020-09-13T14:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T15:04:10.000Z","uid":240362,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"420ecbcab7f44e9b215c933e6c074389f3e42081","tid":2201133,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T14:12:42.000Z","msg":"港島衝鋒隊一名29歲女警被指一腳踏兩船，與隔離組的男警撻着，瞞着拍拖多年的懲教主任男友發展三角戀，男警其後發現自己是第三者，怒火失控打傷女警。事件今年8月被披露後秀茂坪警區重案組第一隊接手調查，並於本月7日將該名男警拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，秀茂坪一名28歲姓蔡休班男警，今年8月18日凌晨懷疑因感情糾紛，與一名29歲女子在秀茂坪曉光街一單位內互相拉扯。最後女方手部受傷，送聯合醫院接受治理。<br />\n<br />\n秀茂坪警區重案組第一隊經進一步調查後，於9月7日上午在秀茂坪區拘捕該名休班警，並控告他一項普通襲擊罪，案件將於9月14日在觀塘裁判法院提堂。警方在整個案情交代中，並未提及該名29歲女子身份。<br />\n<br />\n警方強調，警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍及姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200913/DVREWV7BR5BXLDIE73VSQGTG34/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200913%2FDVREWV7BR5BXLDIE73VSQGTG34%2F&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8JE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=00b98a28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200913%2FDVREWV7BR5BXLDIE73VSQGTG34%2F&h=ffeff5e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200913/DVREWV7BR5BXLDIE73VSQGTG34/</a>"},{"pid":"7b6bb61a2b5ed0feb49011640378e7c974c96d96","tid":2201133,"uid":279333,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T14:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0138564bd044342d3be94dbfec2c163f58ce6330","tid":2201133,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7b6bb61a2b5ed0feb49011640378e7c974c96d96","tid":2201133,"uid":279333,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"repl